			<article class="main container col4">
								<header class="maincol">
										<h1 class="pagetitle">In Graphic Detail: Avian Flu around the World</h1>
										<h2 class="dek singlepagecontainer">Now that it‚Äôs spread rapidly around the globe and jumped to animals such as foxes, sea lions, and cows, scientists worry that the avian flu could spill over to humans.</h2>
										<section class="singlebyline singlepagecontainer">
						<h3 class="invis">Authored by</h3>
						by  
										<a href="https://hakaimagazine.com/profiles/rebecca-heisman/" class="tagmanager" id="author_link_top" >Rebecca Heisman</a>								<br/>
												</section>
					 
					<aside class="singlebydatewords singlepagecontainer">
						<h3 class="invis">Wordcount</h3>
						May 24, 2024 | 450 words, about 3 minutes
					</aside>

					
